ply the provider they need.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"It implements also the protocol ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"ControlItemComponentTokens"},{"text":" so as to expose the component tokens for control-item-layout-basded components through any ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSTheme"},{"text":".","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"Such components tokens are defined with raw and semantic tokens of sizes (from ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"SizeSemanticTokensProvider"},{"text":"),","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"borders (from ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"AllBorderSemanticTokensProvider"},{"text":"),  colors (from ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"AllColorSemanticTokensProvider"},{"text":")  and spaces (from ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"AllSpaceSemanticTokensProvider"},{"text":").","type":"text"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"OrangeThemeControlItemComponentTokensProvider"}],"title":"OrangeThemeControlItemComponentTokensProvider"},"doc://OUDSThemesOrange/documentation/OUDSThemesOrange":{"kind":"symbol","images":[{"identifier":"ic_theme_orange.png","type":"icon"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange","type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/oudsthemesorange","role":"collection","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The Orange theme overrides some tokens from the basic "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSTheme"},{"text":" and should be seen as the default theme for the OUDS library with the Orange brand colors for example.","type":"text"}],"title":"Theme Orange"},"ic_theme_orange.png":{"type":"image","alt":null,"variants":[{"traits":["1x","light"],"url":"\/images\/OUDSThemesOrange\/ic_theme_orange.png"}],"identifier":"ic_theme_orange.png"}}}